de.hsos.ecs.richwps.wpsmonitor.measurement

Class MeasureJob

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hsos.ecs.richwps.wpsmonitor.measurement.MeasureJob
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.quartz.Job

    public class MeasureJob
extends Object
implements org.quartz.Job
    Job class which uses a wps client with a request which is stored in the WpsProcessEntity object to be sent to a Wps Server. The WpsProcessEntity object is injected by the MeasureJobFactory. If no wps exception occurs, then the registred QosProbe instances are called. Otherwise a error flag is set, which is evaluated by the MeasureJobListener. The dependencies should be thread save or new instantiated by the MeasureJobFactory.
    Author:
    Florian Vogelpohl
    See Also:
    WpsProcessEntity, MeasureJobFactory
